# Rhode Island, 0.61% (1,451 votes)

Margin of victory less than 5% (95 electoral votes):
# Massachusetts, 1.09% (17,192 votes)
# New York, 2.35% (103,481 votes)
# Alabama, 2.84% (7,072 votes)
# Texas, 3.67% (26,004 votes)

