==== Close states ====
Margin of victory less than 5% (4 electoral votes):
# New Hampshire, 1.75% (3,818 votes)

Margin of victory greater than 5% but less than 10% (29 electoral votes):
# Kansas, 7.72% (66,793 votes)
# Massachusetts, 9.46% (174,103 votes)
# Delaware, 9.77% (12,466 votes)

Tipping point state:
# Ohio, 20.56% (619,285 votes)

